                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Tavern Challenge: Serious Showdown - Song of the Scorching Loremaster",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Stage Introduction",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "\"Meow.\" \"Sometimes, well-intentioned guests who seek to understand the ways of the desert dwellers are treated with all the appropriate courtesy. Yet the stories of the tribe are many, and ancient beyond reckoning. Attempting to remember some of their more obscure songs in full would be challenging indeed, let alone after only having heart them once...\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(204, 191, 173)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Special Rule: \"Eremite Scorching Loremaster\" starts with the Talent card \"Scorpocalypse\" equipped.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Opposing Lineup",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
